### 11.2.2 因果效用函数的微观基础

由第四章(4.2)，个体![](https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/2443fbcfeb7e85e1d62b6f5e4f27207e.svg)在维度![](https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/756a643380ff53c0692dbc2e7e930a35.svg)上的因果效用为：

![](https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/2c52c6e550aec57a24e6a10e45130e86.svg)

在主角-观众二元分配下：

- 若![](https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/2443fbcfeb7e85e1d62b6f5e4f27207e.svg)为主角，![](https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/04b1df08e3a68e4b87cca63e6c609e1e.svg)
- 若i为观众，a_{i\mu} = 0
- 平均行动水平\bar{a}_\mu = \frac{1}{N_\mu} \sum a_{i\mu} = \frac{K_\mu}{N_\mu} \cdot \frac{K_\mu}{N_\mu} = \left( \frac{K_\mu}{N_\mu} \right)^2

主角的因果效用为：

C_{\text{protag}} = \gamma_\mu \cdot \frac{K_\mu}{N_\mu} \cdot \left( 1 - \left( \frac{K_\mu}{N_\mu} \right)^2 \right)

观众因a_{i\mu} = 0，C_{\text{aud}} = 0。

### 11.2.3 总存在效用的优化

维度\mu内的总因果效用\Gamma_\mu为主角群体的因果效用之和（观众贡献为0，但观众通过弱相对性为主角提供存在感参照——即(1 - \bar{a})项）：

\Gamma_\mu = K_\mu \cdot C_{\text{protag}} = \gamma_\mu K_\mu \cdot \frac{K_\mu}{N_\mu} \left( 1 - \left( \frac{K_\mu}{N_\mu} \right)^2 \right)

令x_\mu = K_\mu / N_\mu \in [0,1]为主角比例。则：

\Gamma_\mu(x_\mu) = \gamma_\mu N_\mu \cdot x_\mu^2 (1 - x_\mu^2) = \gamma_\mu N_\mu (x_\mu^2 - x_\mu^4) \tag{11.1}

### 11.2.4 最优解

对x_\mu求导：

\frac{d\Gamma_\mu}{dx_\mu} = \gamma_\mu N_\mu (2x_\mu - 4x_\mu^3) = 2\gamma_\mu N_\mu x_\mu (1 - 2x_\mu^2)

